dct_description_sm: Campaign brochure produced by the Metuchen Democratic Committee for the 1978 campaigns of Dennis O'Leary and Pat Lagay who were seeking seats on the borough council. This side features photos, biographies and statements from the candidates. There is also a breakdown of the town's spending of tax dollars.
